item.title: Do You Believe In True Love
item.description: C(add9) G Long afternoon walks by the beach C(add9) G Long, long talks about an hour each C(add9) G Driving my bike down your street C(add9) G Hoping to see you, hope that we would meet C(add9) Think of how many things we've been through G And how many places we've been to C(add9) G And that time when we shared our first kiss on that roof I told you piedz.
